{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>近日她上薔薔節目《薔栗膠》，大爆年輕時靠著美色，在夜店走跳「從來沒有花過錢」，還因為容貌出眾，被大咖港星塞紙條，約去飯店續攤。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624182672789504618372.jpeg/XuvO8edL5IoCJx4lwZVdafNTAVdEhlvpdS0plXUtKZU\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><p>更多安歆澐照片：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624345248468992649180.jpeg/Gvgg2aaRyQt29ZH9YmVXR7d0yL5Edx0herdNm3q3TZs\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624346196250624569124.jpeg/g-0apAkFlxNQASOvOWM5JxtFAasM8fgW07Y33tO2N94\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624346108170240931028.jpeg/F_7lLFO9FWCbdcnMuPyLvu2ZJavdNfDYMvfVrDL31aw\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624347526107136935824.jpeg/ASLDS9aBTrNdOWLNRtVfzu1MUuohnGExjoUZq46FGas\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624349740830720293861.jpeg/uIZBOyr6Thca9Yfxz1i_Q5nu0ZbrLqhCr2nBGK9pwRg\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624351103848448738260.jpeg/-Q_VADii0RVH-RqycJWt2YuogKbLCK7M3dwDk93cA5M\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624348478083072374512.jpeg/SyuI1AQOAN2xVPVWJHgutV9Y-IHOIqeQFbTkLhW05C4\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624348444528640298610.jpeg/mqcdpZ0ybrrL8KNJ37gPg_emw25BmDbNVuR5X1bkeV8\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624342979219456036821.jpeg/LE_V_LstE1r6V9H-B2sxdO9DepyiNzWD55-nLOefpyw\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624343604039680036974.jpeg/yWRE220GSMzzs_CmyVI_NCrfRo9YtjaDcK3O9nCtzvY\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624353436012544136970.jpeg/padRAsTHCopgHOAXYoGluGnb9K8SQ_70IrvobyK76G8\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624343813754880810496.jpeg/-OaYexS2swB7Y-k5cMqrw8m9g9qsBntVBDwkFwQ8JBc\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123624340512837632276583.jpeg/s80OFCrSSJn1qmOG7qGgTf7zrRbYPEvL3Fmwe9xZsHs\" alt=\"安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）\"><figcaption>安歆澐（IG@anhsinyun）</figcaption></figure><p>大咖港星看上安歆澐　玩夜店給房間號碼</p><p>安歆澐自述，年輕時在和平東路的夜店玩得相當瘋狂，「你知道我被誰寫過紙條？」主持人薔薔驚訝詢問：「誰？」</p><p>安歆澐提示對方是一個演過香港系列電影的男星，薔薔秒猜《古惑仔》，安歆澐說對，薔薔馬上大喊：</p><p>更多陳小春照片：</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250309/975221339340148736184076.jpeg/1atQhKb2z77CUcSqW_m6Lbak7YIE_Bxq0bw3j9G8N48\" alt=\"陳小春（《97古惑仔戰無不勝》電影劇照）\"><figcaption>陳小春（《97古惑仔戰無不勝》電影劇照）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250508/997218758705811456120385.jpeg/Win-UnT8qzJQttRfYtX9Y0LuiVERwHc7yL27Ksi9uyo\" alt=\"《朝9晚5》由陳小春主演。（《朝9晚5》電影劇照）\"><figcaption>《朝9晚5》由陳小春主演。（《朝9晚5》電影劇照）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250705/1018205671704891392029581.jpeg/wxobAw84zXIStbGDkI96IJ0-8fafWzSqg9tSboPbUm4\" alt=\"《頭文字D》陳小春飾演男配角須藤京一。（《頭文字D》電影劇照）\"><figcaption>《頭文字D》陳小春飾演男配角須藤京一。（《頭文字D》電影劇照）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250125/959818762528231424239768.jpeg/SNRKRusaSsN4AS-SRRBv9lVem4tddQWcjgEMe44BDHs\" alt=\"陳小春（微博圖片）\"><figcaption>陳小春（微博圖片）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250816/1033377089794871296073928.png/rPWswMv7dYSgo8DvZc_i3wu7TGF7M1Sl27s7u9u7O7s\" alt=\"陳小春（影片截圖）\"><figcaption>陳小春（影片截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210817/504380548434497536371685.jpeg/w6sUORPLg3VBOysnKZD5vhNw3obImJAN0R2qNtEdqjY\" alt=\"陳小春。（微博@披荊斬棘的哥哥官微）\"><figcaption>陳小春。（微博@披荊斬棘的哥哥官微）</figcaption></figure><p>薔薔歪打正著講對了，不過這個答案她也不意外，笑說：「沒結婚前誰不是愛玩啊？」安歆澐說陳小春的紙條寫：</p><p>但是她沒有去，一來是她覺得寫紙條很土，再來是「因為我俗仔，他是明星，對我來說很遙遠」。</p><p>【延伸閱讀】「小金城武」約會小兩歲女星遭斷正　以往緋聞對象多為「姐姐型」（點圖放大瀏覽▼▼▼）</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201207/412616254232334336296841.jpeg/zGVGnYGY2x2BAr3M6W1DRN5UF4Es4evkFzTvIxc07yM\" alt=\"【延伸閱讀】「小金城武」約會小兩歲女星遭斷正　以往緋聞對象多為「姐姐型」（IG@chenhaosen802）\"><figcaption>【延伸閱讀】「小金城武」約會小兩歲女星遭斷正　以往緋聞對象多為「姐姐型」（IG@chenhaosen802）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201207/412616252076199936498162.jpeg/VIRhqFKiYNnYG2us5o3sEk49HZBATB-U0GFbyNBhW8g\" alt=\"因演出電影《刻在你心底的名字》人氣爆升的陳昊森， 日前被大陸狗仔拍到與大陸女星蘭西雅甜蜜約會，兩人親密互動就宛如熱戀中，立刻引發網友熱議。 （IG@chenhaosen802）\"><figcaption>因演出電影《刻在你心底的名字》人氣爆升的陳昊森， 日前被大陸狗仔拍到與大陸女星蘭西雅甜蜜約會，兩人親密互動就宛如熱戀中，立刻引發網友熱議。 （IG@chenhaosen802）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260126/1092501318334943232134789.jpeg/FlDcJ59-mtV73NPEK-o9B21CIDNLcIiLTbHC702xwu8\" alt=\"蘭西雅（Instagram@lancia1222）\"><figcaption>蘭西雅（Instagram@lancia1222）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260126/1092496172372725760159846.jpeg/jyJf21TZU2O5WxM7Ml-rLriS-VHCzr_Z3oeR396Hkd8\" alt=\"陳昊森與蘭西雅甜蜜約會。（微博@知名娛記蘇小五）\"><figcaption>陳昊森與蘭西雅甜蜜約會。（微博@知名娛記蘇小五）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260126/1092496174482591744256791.jpeg/DG2H3Lqhno9GhVXC8JMv-SSKx54azLSWmcyOLJnMjiw\" alt=\"陳昊森與蘭西雅甜蜜約會。（微博@知名娛記蘇小五）\"><figcaption>陳昊森與蘭西雅甜蜜約會。（微博@知名娛記蘇小五）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260126/1092496176688926720289051.jpeg/2So4uyxjTJ3_hXhjvSfZmj2MOr923H1v6Kp5ueiqebk\" alt=\"陳昊森與蘭西雅甜蜜約會。（微博@知名娛記蘇小五）\"><figcaption>陳昊森與蘭西雅甜蜜約會。（微博@知名娛記蘇小五）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260126/1092496178782015488702193.jpeg/3r-xcoTdTMspwmaiYtZqcC_cRO_pKh2egGUzw4BlM8M\" alt=\"陳昊森與蘭西雅甜蜜約會。（微博@知名娛記蘇小五）\"><figcaption>陳昊森與蘭西雅甜蜜約會。（微博@知名娛記蘇小五）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260126/1092502011519176704946183.jpeg/GeoCsTyJZ9ilPGing82ok1PdU3RmB3d4ZK6A02SugNM\" alt=\"陳昊森（Instagram@chenhaosen802）\"><figcaption>陳昊森（Instagram@chenhaosen802）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201207/412616250054414336672098.jpeg/e9waljvqOYECAQRniZXIjTf58Kcjd_6fTJ8U-0yfFPs\" alt=\"「小金城武」陳昊森（IG@chenhaosen802）\"><figcaption>「小金城武」陳昊森（IG@chenhaosen802）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201207/412616248124903424590271.jpeg/Ff0FCPU493Vz7uQqvyL06npZ2ZbDOorucQuSZXELkmU\" alt=\"「小金城武」陳昊森（IG@chenhaosen802）\"><figcaption>「小金城武」陳昊森（IG@chenhaosen802）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201207/412616242248421376617203.jpeg/U7xy4adw4qyyQzMKdh1G3uNXhZsTcwiiVyT6Z1ck-mc\" alt=\"「小金城武」陳昊森（IG@chenhaosen802）\"><figcaption>「小金城武」陳昊森（IG@chenhaosen802）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201207/412616244446367744705429.jpeg/rPYHxswTQkUzKew6MnqmmptsAQ_nJUYTNRVG3DUVRtw\" alt=\"「小金城武」陳昊森（IG@chenhaosen802）\"><figcaption>「小金城武」陳昊森（IG@chenhaosen802）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/202012